<div class="flex flex-col gap-10 py-8 lg:flex-row">
  <!-- Left Box (Info) -->
  <div
    class="w-full rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg shadow-gray-400 dark:shadow-gray-900 lg:w-1/2"
    style="background: url('../GreenEyes.svg');   
    background-size: 70px 80px; /* Adjust size */
    background-position: center; /* Center the pattern */
    background-repeat: repeat;"
  >
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Food Is A Human Right</h3>
    <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-gray-200">
      Our mission is clear: to make nutritious food accessible and affordable
      for everyone. We believe that access to healthy food is a fundamental
      human right—not a privilege.
    </p>

    <!-- Mini Call to Action -->
    <div class="mt-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-100">
        Join us in building a sustainable future where everyone has access to
        fresh, affordable, and nourishing food.
      </p>
      <div
        class="mt-8 flex flex-col space-y-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center sm:space-x-4 sm:space-y-0"
      >
        <!-- Membership Button -->
        <a
          href="/membership"
          class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-6 py-4 font-bold text-white hover:bg-accent-600 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent-300"
        >
          Become a Member
        </a>
        <!-- Contact Button -->
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-primary-500 px-6 py-4 font-bold text-white hover:bg-primary-600 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-300"
        >
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Right Box (Statistics) -->
  <div
    class="w-full rounded-lg p-6 shadow-lg shadow-gray-400 dark:shadow-gray-900 lg:w-1/2"
    style="background: url('../OrangeEyes.svg');     
      background-size: 70px 80px; /* Adjust size */
      background-position: center; /* Center the pattern */
      background-repeat: repeat;"
  >
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Key Statistics</h3>
    <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-gray-100">
      <li>🍎 40% of food in the U.S. goes uneaten.</li>
      <li>🌍 30% of food is wasted globally each year.</li>
      <li>🥦 Factory-farmed veggies can have up to 40% fewer nutrients.</li>
      <li>💧 1 pound of beef requires 1,800 gallons of water.</li>
      <li>🌾 Approximately 7 pounds of feed produces just 1 pound of beef.</li>
      <li>🐄 Livestock farming accounts for 14.5% of global emissions.</li>
      <li>💡 Food waste accounts for 8% of global greenhouse gas emissions.</li>
      <li>🚜 Reducing food waste by just 25% could feed 870 million people.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
